<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1107">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$lin-jun-yu-76" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/lin-jun-yu-76" class="zg-link" title="林俊宇">林俊宇</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$da-mo-cang-lang-78" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/da-mo-cang-lang-78" class="zg-link" title="冯震山">冯震山</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


